commit 64e95b0cb69004d49a4353b7dd7dcf5ba2ba218f
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Tue Apr 7 05:37:52 2026 +0000

    Add mw-wiki-push-backup script to push git-modified wiki pages

    Provides a way to push locally modified wiki backup files back to the
    wiki using mw-edit. Uses git diff to detect which .mw files changed,
    converts filenames back to page titles, and pushes each one.

    Supports --dry-run, --edit-msg, and --git-diff-arg options.

    https://claude.ai/code/session_01SDVqu7FG7gUS4zScL4ZCKX

