commit ab32019fc0a395d7663b32c55678b726f6c26d19
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Mon Apr 6 08:29:06 2026 +0000

    simplify: remove unnecessary bash compatibility workaround for empty array

    Debian Trixie ships Bash 5.2+ which handles empty array expansion
    correctly with set -o nounset.

    https://claude.ai/code/session_011pjrpk19yJsa2Wyiq88Lp6

commit d9dd358dd07af06dc79e49377bb9b29e7c6aa9cb
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Mon Apr 6 08:21:12 2026 +0000

    fix: add article sanity test for Widget:CodeSelect in backup scripts

    Ensures backups verify that Widget:CodeSelect is present in the fetched
    page list, catching cases where Widget namespace pages are missing.

    https://claude.ai/code/session_011pjrpk19yJsa2Wyiq88Lp6

commit 6b992b87762f19870f0108ce31ec7c2b65ab8857
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Mon Apr 6 08:17:31 2026 +0000

    fix: pass Widget (274) and Moved (500) namespaces through backup pipeline

    The site-specific backup scripts now pass --namespace-extra-list="274 500"
    to mw-process-all-pages, which in turn forwards article-sanity-test,
    namespace-default-list, and namespace-extra-list options through to
    mw-all-pages. This ensures Widget namespace pages (e.g. Widget:Icon_Bullet_List)
    are included in backups.

    Reverts 274 from default_namespace_default_list in mw-all-pages since these
    are site-specific namespaces that belong in the specific backup scripts.

    https://claude.ai/code/session_011pjrpk19yJsa2Wyiq88Lp6

commit 37507512354a8d7e1c420ad41871d7353cc41eef
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Mon Apr 6 08:00:12 2026 +0000

    fix: add Widget namespace (274) to default backup namespace list

    Widget namespace pages (e.g. Widget:Icon_Bullet_List) were missing from
    backups because namespace 274 was not included in
    default_namespace_default_list. The namespace was acknowledged in a
    comment but never actually added to the list.

    https://claude.ai/code/session_011pjrpk19yJsa2Wyiq88Lp6

